"title": "5790: anger, divine",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5790",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The anger of God is directed against all human sin, disobedience, rebellion and wickedness, which threaten to thwart his purposes for his creation and people.</p>\n<h2>Causes of divine anger</h2>\n<h3>Disobedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:24-Isa5:25\">ISA 5:24–5:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:22\">NUM 22:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:1\">JOS 7:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:13\">2KI 22:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:21-Ps78:22\">PSA 78:21–78:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:15\">MIC 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:12\">ZEC 7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:5\">MRK 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:5\">ROM 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:5-Eph5:6\">EPH 5:5–5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:7-Heb3:12\">HEB 3:7–3:12</a></p>\n<h3>Sinfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:17\">ISA 57:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:46\">1KI 8:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:9\">1KI 11:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr19:2\">2CH 19:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:25\">2CH 32:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:1-Eph2:3\">EPH 2:1–2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:5-Col3:6\">COL 3:5–3:6</a></p>\n<h3>Apostasy and idolatry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:3\">NUM 25:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:25\">DEU 4:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:8\">DEU 9:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:18\">JOS 22:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:16\">JOS 23:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:19-Judg2:20\">JDG 2:19–2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg10:6-Judg10:7\">JDG 10:6–10:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:15\">1KI 14:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:17\">2KI 22:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:14\">EZR 9:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:17-Jer7:18\">JER 7:17–7:18</a></p>\n<h2>The characteristics of God that provoke his anger</h2>\n<h3>He is a holy God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:11\">PSA 7:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:19-Josh24:20\">JOS 24:19–24:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:10\">JER 10:10</a></p>\n<h3>He is a jealous God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:15\">DEU 6:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:22\">1KI 14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:5\">PSA 79:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:38\">EZK 16:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:2\">NAM 1:2</a></p>\n<h3>He is the universal judge</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:6\">PSA 79:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:22\">EZR 8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:2\">ISA 34:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:8\">ZEP 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>He is also compassionate and slow to anger</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:8\">PSA 103:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:6\">EXO 34:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:17\">NEH 9:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:38\">PSA 78:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:15\">PSA 86:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:2\">JON 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:3\">NAM 1:3</a></p>\n<h2>Consequences of divine anger</h2>\n<h3>Death and destruction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:8\">DEU 9:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:7\">EXO 15:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:10-Exod32:11\">EXO 32:10–32:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:1-Num11:2\">NUM 11:1–11:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:9\">JOB 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:5\">ISA 13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:29\">JER 32:29</a></p>\n<h3>Present judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:2\">LAM 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:13\">NUM 32:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:3\">2KI 13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:20\">ISA 51:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:8\">EZK 7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:12\">HAB 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:12-Matt21:13\">MAT 21:12–21:13</a></p>\n<h3>Future judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:9\">ISA 13:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:19\">DAN 8:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:7\">MAT 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:5\">ROM 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>God's rejection of his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:29\">JER 7:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:17\">DEU 31:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:18\">2KI 17:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:25-2Kgs23:27\">2KI 23:25–23:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:59\">PSA 78:59</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:38\">PSA 89:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:6-Lam2:7\">LAM 2:6–2:7</a></p>\n<h2>Being saved from the anger of God</h2>\n<h3>God's anger may be temporary</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:5\">PSA 30:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:9\">PSA 103:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:8\">ISA 54:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:16\">ISA 57:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:10\">ISA 60:10</a></p>\n<h3>God's anger cannot be averted by human means</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:18\">ZEP 1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:4\">PRO 11:4</a></p>\n<h3>Humility and repentance are required</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:3\">ZEP 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:30-Gen18:32\">GEN 18:30–18:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:18-Deut9:19\">DEU 9:18–9:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:7\">2CH 12:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:12\">2CH 12:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:8\">2CH 30:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:9\">ISA 64:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:13\">JOL 2:13</a></p>\n<h3>God's anger is averted on account of his love for believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:22\">LAM 3:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:9\">HOS 11:9</a></p>\n<h3>God's anger is averted on account of the work of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:9\">ROM 5:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:36\">JHN 3:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:10\">1TH 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:9\">1TH 5:9</a></p>",
